data.description: Welcome to your dream retreat just minutes from the interstate! Situated on a nice 2.25-acre lot, this charming home offers comfort, space, and convenience. This home has 4 beds, and 3 baths, with a half basement with plenty of storage! Enjoy a separate master suite from the other 3 bedrooms, perfect for the parents and the kids! This house also includes a fenced-in backyard, front and back porches, and a carport! Experience country living with convenience. Call your favorite realtor and set up a showing today! A video walkthrough is available
